snippet.title: Demonetisation: Peoples Put Shoes, Slippers to Reserve Their Place in Queue

localized.description:
Demonetisation: Peoples put shoes and slippers to reserve their places in queues outside ATMs and banks. Peoples are struggling to exchange, deposit and withdraw cash after ban on Rs 500 and Rs 1000
